text: Ay () is a rural locality (a village) in Alegazovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 33 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 7 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 6 km from Alegazovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Ay, Republic of Bashkortostan
